data.description: Back on the market, sold as is, and priced substantially below current market value. Take advantage of this excellent opportunity to own the sought-after community of Idlewild Village with its state-of-the-art community center and beautiful neighborhood with its extraordinary landscapes,  including the tranquil trails, sidewalks, and curves throughout this impressive neighborhood. This stunning brick-front home features a gas fireplace, family room,  formal living and dining rooms, a granite countertop kitchen, a fully finished basement with a full bath, dual closets in the primary bedroom, a two-car garage, recessed light, and much more. Close to I95, shopping, schools, Downtown Fredericksburg, and commuter lots. Available immediately, the seller will consider a lease with the option to own and is willing to assist with closing.
